Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:09.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I entered middle school when I was twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:16.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In ninth grade I applied for Kitahoro High School, since it was nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:25.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then in the spring of my fifteenth year, I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:31.70,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,“If only I could be like Kazehaya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:34.57,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}Maybe then something will change for me too.”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:39.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:55.30,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been the first step for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:04.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year was too different for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:08.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take too long to describe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:28.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I guess that was boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:32.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to have a different vibe next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.20,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,You already do, for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:38.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're easier to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:40.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:43.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.07,0:02:47.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:51.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to ruin the makeup Ayane-chan did for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:55.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three seconds, wait three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:55.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:08.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always had a good vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:12.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were smiling, even before the entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you gave me directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:22.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we were in the same class,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:27.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I haven't seen you smile like that since.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:31.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering what kind of person you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:39.92,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd remember when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:44.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be a good person,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:47.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but more than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,More?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:56.77,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can assume he thinks I'm a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:04:00.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You changed a lot today too; you scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:06.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry. I didn't mean to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:09.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:22.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's line up to visit the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:33.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,You already do, for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:39.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:45.92,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,You wished you were cute when you met Kurumi, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:51.22,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about why you want to be cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:57.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayane-chan, there's only one answer to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:07.12,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,You were cuter than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:13.42,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to want to be more like Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:19.55,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I want him to think I'm cute, if only just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:27.71,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:32.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are we doing this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:37.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until Joe gets bored of Yano-chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:41.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:43.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:45.92,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:51.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joe, your down jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:55.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like it? I just bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:06:00.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably full of holes from the sparks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:07.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what about the shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:11.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:13.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:19.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't really explain why you dragged him around, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:21.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:26.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yano-chin. I'll hook you up with ramen next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:28.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll get fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:34.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But now we're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:36.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:39.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you ditch us like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:41.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it got lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't put up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:49.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you be a bit more friendly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:54.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try saying Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:03.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make you smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:07.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,however Kuronuma acts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:09.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if they bump into someone they know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:11.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouta will figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:14.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:15.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:17.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're having too much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:20.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:24.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't think you need to worry about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:39.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to have sweet sake and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're visiting the shrine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.11,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:54.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five, four, three, two, one
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:58.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy new year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:02.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:04.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Best regards for the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:09.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You too, best regards for the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.25,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:17.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you receive a text?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two even.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:29.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're from Chizu-chan and Ayane-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:33.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:34.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:40.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy-new-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:45.71,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They beat me to texting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having fun. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:56.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:02.77,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Best regards for the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:13.36,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So much of what happened last year were firsts for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our turn, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:23.58,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,All the things I thought about,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:27.16,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,all the things I experienced...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:39.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because I met all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:47.34,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It became an unforgettable year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:50.01,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's slippery here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's coming over on New Year's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:42.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember her name yet, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.28,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:49.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to be your sister-in-law soon, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:05.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu, if something ever happens to you, I'll comfort you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:14.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:26.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see what our fortunes will be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Very Good.”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:43.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“All will be as you wish.”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:48.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Beware of your temper; be composed and approach everything with calmness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take heed of the advice of others.”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I do that, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:05.07,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably not Very G—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:16.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I expected too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:20.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm too greedy these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:21.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma, what did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:25.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:38.29,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The best...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.36,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:44.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard “Bad” is actually pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's not too common.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:47.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:51.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to hang these up on trees, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:55.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:58.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Very Good" you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:06.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:11.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'd absorb your good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:15.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always had good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:20.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:24.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:32.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sort of a shabby birthday present, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:45.16,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Hesitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.09,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have any?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:58.12,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think of it, I don't know why I wasn't sure I liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:08.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,How did I see him only with admiration all that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:20.63,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I spent New Year's Eve with Ayane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:27.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd be at the bonfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about my idiot of a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:34.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going home, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:37.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:38.66,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,All these holes in your jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:40.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting any new year's allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:42.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:46.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:59.21,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear God, please erase the fact that I spent New Year's Eve with Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:02.11,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I ask for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:15.96,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They're getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:19.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I won't need to get my fortune then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:25.98,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, they really look like a normal couple when they're like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:32.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:36.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Come on. Let's go drink a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So many idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:43.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Tohru were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:46.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd score with some totally random pick-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:50.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard says he's going to his girlfriend's for the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:53.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marriage my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:55.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look him in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.61,0:15:58.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:15:59.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:04.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't people tell you you're cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:15.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your e-mail address.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything to say about guys with glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,...see success!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:30.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be together in our next lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:37.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tha—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:43.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you think you're good enough to get picked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:47.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that idiot from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:53.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:55.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:57.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, stop getting led on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:58.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:00.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:02.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:04.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're embarrassing me, go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:50.00,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Past this hill...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:57.00,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the usual way to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.65,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:06.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I first met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:20.36,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What will this year be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:40.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:48.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you see that empty house?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're there too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:54.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:19:00.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:02.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't leave me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:11.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kurumi, did you make a wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you write?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:13.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:16.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:18.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:26.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:27.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:33.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:34.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:36.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spending the new year together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:42.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we hang out together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:45.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:20:00.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Sawako coming home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:02.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:05.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, it's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:14.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:16.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:51.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:04.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:06.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:40.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can change my temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:44.87,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:55.91,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,“Relationships — Offer your love. Happiness awaits.”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:21:59.20,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,“Classmate,”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:08.82,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,“Guy next to me in class”—but not my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:20.83,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's more distant than a friend, and I want him to be more than a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:26.73,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,“Someone I like.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:26.62,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to know if it's for eternity or not
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:34.55,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could live like this forever, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:45.47,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be like those paper airplanes filling the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:53.82,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,and I will find only one
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:19:08.29,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, love grows with being needed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:22.41,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could smile and enjoy the distance between us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:31.13,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell you the thoughts he accumulated
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:45.33,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do in a world like that where nobody notices me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:50.27,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to know if it's for eternity or not
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:56.79,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could live like this forever, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:20:08.87,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be like those paper airplanes filling the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:16.65,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:26.46,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,If the two of us accepted each other more
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:33.03,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me just a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:39.07,KimiTodo-Meta,,0000,0000,0000,,Flower of love blowing in the wind
